metadata.name: CypherGoool Chronicles GooolDisc
metadata.description:
2022 - Against the backdrop of a highly surveilled future, goools must develop and use trustless technology to freely share information and verify against malicious artificial clones that have infiltrated the general population.

--------

Edition of 100

eGOOOLx is the special features and extras collection for the eGOOOL collection by elle (riotgoools.eth)

--------

Riot Goools, along with the Magical/Power/Creepy/Weird Goools and Gooolmon, are natives of the Fantom Network. The expanded Gooolniverse includes Goools on XTZ on Tezos and CypherGoool Chronicles on Ethereum.
